===Lalawigan===
{{main articles|[[Provinces of Spain]] and [[Comarcas of Spain]]}}

Ing ka-arian Espanya ing pangatatag na, makadake yang lalawigan.  Atin yang 50 [[Lalawigan|lalawigan]] o (''probinsiya''). Iting pangatatag bayu ya kareng autonomous communities at makapetsa manibat kanitang 1833. Ngeni, deng autonomous a komunidad a aptas a lalawigan antimo ing  [[Extremadura]] atin yang aduang lalawigan: [[Cáceres |Cáceres]] at [[Badajoz|Badajoz]]). Ding autnomous a komunidad a [[Asturias]], ing [[Pulung Balearic]], [[Cantabria]], [[La Rioja]], [[Navarre]], [[Murcia]], at [[Madrid]] ing bangsang [[Balen tungku|tungku]]) a atin lang tunggal a lalawigan.  Keng makalumang kaugalian deng lalawigan keraklan makadake lang agpang keng kasalesalayan a labuad a ausan dang ''comarcas''.

===Makasariling Communidad===
[[Image:ccaa-spain.png|thumb|400px|Autonomous communities of Spain]]
{{main|Autonomous communities of Spain}}
Spain consists of 17 autonomous communities (''comunidades autónomas'') and 2 autonomous cities (''ciudades autónomas''; [[Ceuta]] and [[Melilla]]).
* [[Andalusia]] (''Andalucía'')
* [[Aragon]] (''Aragón'')
